al)\n- Risks identified (ACs that seem untestable, unclear requirements, missing dependencies)\n- Observations (anything surprising or noteworthy about this story)\nIf nothing to report, write `## Session Issues\\n\\nNone.`\n\nMANDATORY — Also end your response with a `## Token Report` section:\n- Total tool calls: N\n- By tool: Bash: X, Read: Y, Edit: Z, Grep: W, Write: V, other: N\n- Largest Bash outputs (top 3 by line count): command (~N lines each)\n- Files read: N unique, M total reads (list any file read 3+ times)\n- Redundant operations: describe any repeated reads, duplicate commands, or wasted calls","subagent_type":"general-purpose"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":743,"cache_read_input_tokens":42687,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":743},"output_tokens":40,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f19e005-5742-4a5a-a61f-d8a88dc16bec","uuid":"0b06f1c2-99f2-4ad9-84e2-e3724267a5b8"}
