{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01L6Q51N1sFQ6xF6CTJjHZGg","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Story 13.2: Output Contract Prompt Injection\n2\t\n3\tStatus: ready-for-dev\n4\t\n5\t<!-- Note: Validation is optional. Run validate-create-story for quality check before dev-story. -->\n6\t\n7\t## Story\n8\t\n9\tAs a developer,\n10\tI want the previous task's output contract injected into the next task's prompt,\n11\tso that cross-framework tasks have context from the previous step.\n12\t\n13\t## Acceptance Criteria\n14\t\n15\t1. **Given** a new `formatContractAsPromptContext(contract: OutputContract): string` function in `src/lib/agents/output-contract.ts`\n16\t   **When** called with a valid `OutputContract`\n17\t   **Then** it returns a structured text block containing: changed files list, test results summary, output summary, and AC statuses\n18\t   **And** the formatted string is human-readable and parseable by any LLM\n19\t   <!-- verification: test-provable -->\n20\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f19e005-5742-4a5a-a61f-d8a88dc16bec","uuid":"984207af-a3b8-4a6d-bd22-e1e59b0c26a0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T10:27:57.118Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/13-2-output-contract-prompt-injection.md","content":"# Story 13.2: Output Contract Prompt Injection\n\nStatus: ready-for-dev\n\n<!-- Note: Validation is optional. Run validate-create-story for quality check before dev-story. -->\n\n## Story\n\nAs a developer,\nI want the previous task's output contract injected into the next task's prompt,\nso that cross-framework tasks have context from the previous step.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. **Given** a new `formatContractAsPromptContext(contract: OutputContract): string` function in `src/lib/agents/output-contract.ts`\n   **When** called with a valid `OutputContract`\n   **Then** it returns a structured text block containi